      • addToWikiField

        public Process addToWikiField(String message,
                              Process process)
        The addMessageToWikiField() method is a helper method which composes the new wiki field using a StringBuilder. The message is encoded using HTML entities to prevent certain characters from playing merry havoc when the message box shall be rendered in a browser later.
        Parameters:
        message - the message to append

      • addToWikiField

        public String addToWikiField(String level,
                             String message,
                             Process process)
        The method addToWikiField() adds a message with a given level to the wiki field of the process. Four level strings will be recognized and result in different colors:
        debug
        gray
        error
        red
        user
        green
        warn
        orange
        any other value
        blue
        Parameters:
        level - message colour, one of: "debug", "error", "info", "user" or "warn"; any other value defaults to "info"
        message - text

      • addToWikiField

        public void addToWikiField(User user,
                           String message,
                           Process process)
        The method addToWikiField() adds a message signed by the given user to the wiki field of the process.
        Parameters:
        user - to sign the message with
        message - to print
